'''圣雅各堂'''（St James' Church）是英国[[利物浦|利物浦]]的一座[[圣公会|圣公会]]教堂，位于[[托克斯泰斯|托克斯泰斯]]圣雅各坊。该堂建于1774-1775年，在1974年10月1日宣布废弃<ref>{{Citation| publication-date = | date = | year = 2011| title = Diocese of Liverpool: All Schemes| series = Church Commissioners/Statistics| publisher = Church of England| page = 4| format = PDF| url = http://www.churchofengland.org/media/810716/liverpool.pdf| accessdate = 2011-12-06| archive-date = 2012-05-16| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120516141721/http://www.churchofengland.org/media/810716/liverpool.pdf| dead-url = no}}</ref>，2010年5月恢复使用<ref>{{Citation| url = http://www.stjamesinthecity.org.uk/about-us/building-project.html| title = Building Project| accessdate = 2011-12-06| publisher = Church of St James in the City, Liverpool| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120426030440/http://www.stjamesinthecity.org.uk/about-us/building-project.html| archivedate = 2012-04-26}}</ref>。1985年列为II*级[[登录建筑|登录建筑]]<ref name=nhl>{{NHLE |num= 1209882 |desc= Church of St James, Liverpool|access-date= 2011-12-06 |mode=cs2}}</ref>。 

内部的建筑风格为乔治式。<ref name=pev/> 该堂有18世纪早期和19世纪早期纪念碑。<ref name=pev>{{Citation | last =Pollard| first =Richard | author2 =Nikolaus Pevsner| series= The Buildings of England|title =Lancashire: Liverpool and the South-West |edition= | publisher =[[Yale_University_Press|Yale University Press]] | year =2006 | location =New Haven and London | page = 470| isbn =0-300-10910-5 }}</ref>许多纪念碑涉及到[[大西洋奴隶贸易|奴隶贸易]]。

